headline.print_headline: Italian Exhibit Commemorates World War I Centenary
headline.main: Italian Exhibit Commemorates World War I Centenary

lead_paragraph: Previously unpublished World War I images and documents are on display at Italy's Tomb of the Unknown Soldier starting Saturday, commemorating the 100th anniversary of the bloody conflict that many historians say united Italians in common cause for the first time.
